: 239, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 81430, "content": "以为正义可以战胜一切", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620353}, {"id": 81175, "content": "真的要写再努力也没有用的时候，发现会问自己：你真的努力了吗？不管是命运还是爱情！", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 562962}, {"id": 81431, "content": "找一个和你不怎么像你的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 562352}]}